activeQuests.name: 616052ea3054fc0e2c24ce6e name 54cb50c76803fa8b248b4571
activeQuests.description: I have a mission for you. I need you to eliminate some trash from Tarkov's streets. You up for it?
activeQuests.successMessageText: A damn beast you are, hehe. Good work, here's your share.

activeQuests.name: 616041eb031af660100c9967 name 58330581ace78e27b8b10cee
activeQuests.description: Ah, mercenary, do you want to do a good deed? My clients are asking to ensure a safe area to conduct a specific secret operation. I would like to appoint you for this, as you are the most competent of the local workers. You will have to survey the area and report back to me. Good luck.
activeQuests.successMessageText: Marvelous, young man. Thank you for some fine work.

activeQuests.name: 61604635c725987e815b1a46 name 58330581ace78e27b8b10cee

activeQuests.successMessageText: There you are! You got everything? Good stuff.
